News Releases, Media Advisories

Mary 14, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON LAROUCHE’S COMMITTEE FOR A NEW BRETTON WOODS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on LaRouche’s Committee for a new Bretton Woods. This audit covers the period of September 10, 1997 through September 30, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on LaRouche's Committee for a New Bretton Woods
